🎬 PlaylistPal – Videos & Playlists

"This is a youtube downloader videos and the part you've been wanting the downloading the playlists."

Download YouTube videos or entire playlists straight to your computer – easy, fast, and fun! 🚀

# 🛠 INSTALL PACKAGES
    `npm install`

▶️ RUN THE APP
    `npm run dev`

# ⚙️ CONFIGURE DOWNLOAD FOLDERS

`"Edit this line to your desired directory"`

# Open the script and edit these variables:

`const BASE_DIR = "/home/mjuste/Music/"; // for single videos`
`const BASE_DIR_PLAYLIST = "/home/mjuste/Music/"; // for playlists`

Change them to wherever you want your videos and playlists to go.

# 📥 DOWNLOAD VIDEOS OR PLAYLISTS

`"Paste the link of your youtube vidoe or playlist."`

# Run the app:

 `npm run dev`

# Paste the YouTube video or playlist URL when prompted.

Watch the magic happen – videos will download right into your chosen folder! ✨


Sit back, relax, and enjoy your downloaded videos and playlists! 🥳


Made with ❤️ by **Juste**

